Package jrigby.openstack_queue.request_templates

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ThreeStageJobInterface
    Defines the three stages used in a three-stage job
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ThreeStageJobCallback
    Partial implementation of a three-stage callback.
    ThreeStageJobCallbackImpl
    A full implementation of ThreeStageJobCallback where the three stages are supplied as String arguments for remote execution.
    ThreeStageJobResourceRequest
    A ResourceRequest that includes the ThreeStageJobCallbackImpl callback.
    ThreeStageJobResourceRequestJsonMessage
    This class provides a convenient way to safely convert json into a ThreeStageJobResourceRequest.
